{
  "stem": "23737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they paid large amounts of money to the Germans because they were promised that they will be exchanged with Switzerland for trucks, and ammunition, and I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the first group went from Budapest a few weeks before us, went to Belsen, and they were exchanged at the, I think the first week of December.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my friend's sister was in that first group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When we were taken, by then there were only a handful of people who paid money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The rest were just like myself and others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't pay anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we were taken to that camp as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was called the sonderlager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And all of the time, we were told that we will be exchanged for trucks and medicines with Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the time hasn't come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we were never exchanged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we wore our own clothes all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We didn't get the striped clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we had a little bit more food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had a piece of bread every day for instance-- what the other camps didn't have.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had a piece of bread and black coffee in the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we had a plate of soup at lunchtime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So that was our food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was quite lucky because on the train already, I met a friend of my mother's.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when we arrived to Belsen, she realized that a relation of her husband's was running the office, because every camp had their own offices.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Our camp had their own office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was working in the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that meant that she had her piece of bread in the office.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what she got in the camp-- that was mine as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had two pieces of bread every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
